&lt;li&gt;A great agile and intercultural work environment, including flat hierarchies, an open-door policy, a focus on empowerment, joint responsibility, and mutual trust and support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working with a skilled, high-achieving, experienced, fun, international, and growing team—with lots of opportunities to develop your professional career, take on further responsibilities, and grow with the company&lt;/li&gt;
