&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the platform architecture&lt;/strong&gt; — Define how BSPs, Yocto layers, distros, and reference images fit together. Identify where complexity is accidental versus necessary, and act on it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be the customer&#39;s technical advocate&lt;/strong&gt; — Engage with customers beyond support tickets: understand what&#39;s blocking them, and bring that signal back into platform decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead and grow the team&lt;/strong&gt; — Mentor engineers at different levels, help them make better architectural decisions, and build a culture of ownership and engineering excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive cross-functional strategy&lt;/strong&gt; — Shape release strategy and long-term platform direction alongside BSP, security, CI, and product teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Represent Toradex externally&lt;/strong&gt; — Share knowledge through technical writing, webinars, and customer engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
