&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;708&quot; data-local-id=&quot;c4cfd1e82116&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Security feature enablement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;739&quot; data-local-id=&quot;ba7bc5a2b220&quot;&gt;Bring up security features on new hardware. Every new product we release, we strive to have a uniform, straightforward experience for enabling basic hardware security features like secure boot, ARM TrustZone/&lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_kqswh2mm&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_5pioz8co _189e1dm9 _1il9buyh _19lc184f _d0altlke&quot; data-testid=&quot;definition-highlighter&quot;&gt;OP-TEE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, and hardware-backed encryption.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;990&quot; data-local-id=&quot;8656058b34fd&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;System-level hardening&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1016&quot; data-local-id=&quot;59051cce3d49&quot;&gt;Toradex maintains Torizon OS, a secure, production-ready embedded Linux OS. Making sure that security features fit into the whole stack, and that configurations are secure-by-default for the most common and supported workflows is a key part of the job. Understanding how everything fits together is a must.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1326&quot; data-local-id=&quot;5c624b5e60f7&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Vulnerability management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1354&quot; data-local-id=&quot;56236ecdbb3a&quot;&gt;Monitor upstream CVEs, assess their impact on Toradex products and their likely impact on Toradex customers&#39; products. Apply patches and mitigations. Help draft security advisories and write VEX documents. Work on and maintain internal tooling for vulnerability management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1631&quot; data-local-id=&quot;2e0dab4cc4bb&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Security testing and automation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Toradex&lt;/strong&gt; is a global company strongly focused on engineering &amp;amp; technology. We’re powered by a diverse &amp;amp; uniquely gifted workforce. We pursue the best people to propel our innovative vision of embedded computing and IoT. If you’re interested in being a driving force at an agile technology company, engineering clever computing solutions &amp;amp; helping other companies bring their products to life, we should talk.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Toradex Solutions Inc. is a premier provider of high-tech electronics design, full-cycle product development, and manufacturing services in the GTA. Our integrated in-house capabilities support customers across North America and Europe in bringing innovative products to market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a detail-oriented &lt;strong&gt;Program Coordinator&lt;/strong&gt; to support project planning, material readiness, fulfillment, and execution across customer programs. This role plays an important part in helping prototype and MVP builds progress smoothly through to successful customer delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the Operations &amp;amp; Manufacturing Manager, this role is well suited to a candidate with experience in project coordination, manufacturing operations, order fulfillment, or program support who is looking to grow within a dynamic and collaborative environment. The ideal candidate brings strong coordination skills, attention to detail, and a proactive approach to follow-up, along with an eagerness to learn modern agentic tools and digital visualization tools that support reporting, visibility, and decision-making.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will collaborate closely with Production, SMT &amp;amp; Assembly, Engineering, Sales, Supply Chain, Finance, and leadership teams locally and internationally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Program Planning &amp;amp; Execution Coordination&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support program plans, schedules, milestones, and execution activities for prototype, MVP, and customer delivery initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track timelines, action items, dependencies, and risks to help maintain alignment across cross-functional teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate routine status reviews, reporting, and follow-up activities to maintain visibility across active programs and priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate project records in ERP, Excel, or internal systems, including schedules, open actions, and status updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify potential delays, resource gaps, or execution risks and escalate concerns in a timely manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the use of standardized coordination practices and tools to promote consistent program execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supply Chain Coordination &amp;amp; Material Planning&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support material planning and supply readiness activities for prototype, MVP, and customer delivery timelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with supply chain, production, and engineering teams to track component availability, shortages, lead times, and material-related risks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in providing backup support for procurement activities, including purchasing priorities and material requirements aligned with build plans and project schedules.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor inbound supply status and coordinate follow-up on material issues that could affect build readiness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain visibility of material readiness and communicate supply constraints, changes, and risks to relevant stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Order Fulfillment Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare fulfillment trackers, order status upd

