&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;240&quot; data-local-id=&quot;d20e55bd6e7e&quot;&gt;Toradex is a global company strongly focused on engineering and technology and a leader in embedded computing. We provide hardware and software building blocks (System on Modules, carrier boards and our Torizon platform) to industrial, medical, automotive and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_kqswh2mm&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_5pioz8co _189e1dm9 _1il9buyh _19lc184f _d0altlke&quot; data-testid=&quot;definition-highlighter&quot;&gt;IoT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;companies. Our products are used in demanding applications such as medical devices, industrial automation, smart agriculture, robotics and transportation.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Are you a tech-savvy finance professional who loves to bridge the gap between complex data infrastructure and strategic decision-making? We are seeking a highly analytical and forward-thinking &lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Senior &lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;FP&amp;amp;A&lt;/span&gt; Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; to, as part of the team Finance Business Partnering and &lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;FP&amp;amp;A&lt;/span&gt;, elevate our financial planning, analysis, and business intelligence capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1019&quot; data-local-id=&quot;4fb3b351e129&quot;&gt;Moving far beyond traditional, static reporting, this senior role acts as a strategic partner to management. You will drive our data strategy, build sophisticated data models, and champion the transition toward predictive analytics. Operating as a senior &lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;FP&amp;amp;A&lt;/span&gt; analyst, you don&#39;t just run the numbers—you challenge the status quo, proactively propose solutions to complex cross-departmental challenges, and mentor less experienced colleagues to foster a data-driven culture.&lt;/p&gt;
