&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1561&quot; data-local-id=&quot;75eece8c61d1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Challenge the Status Quo:&lt;/strong&gt; Actively identify alternative and better ways of financial reporting, budgeting, and forecasting to optimize management information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1561&quot; data-local-id=&quot;75eece8c61d1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Cross-Functional Alignment:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate effectively with team members, line managers, and global departments (such as IT, Operations, and Sales) to ensure alignment on KPIs and strategic initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Toradex&lt;/strong&gt; is a global company strongly focused on engineering &amp;amp; technology. We’re powered by a diverse &amp;amp; uniquely gifted workforce. We pursue the best people to propel our innovative vision of embedded computing and IoT. If you’re interested in being a driving force at an agile technology company, engineering clever computing solutions &amp;amp; helping other companies bring their products to life, we should talk.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you’ll own the day-to-day shipping and receiving flow for our Seattle fulfillment center. This is an office-based operation handling small, high-value electronic components (not a traditional warehouse). We’re looking for someone who takes pride in doing things correctly, communicates clearly, and has a growth mindset - this role is very learnable for a bright, computer-literate person who “owns” their work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process incoming and outgoing shipments (domestic and international) with a high level of accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Receive and inspect incoming goods; enter receipts and movements accurately in Microsoft Dynamics 365&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare shipping documentation, labels, and customs paperwork as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process customer returns and coordinate with internal teams to resolve issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate inventory through good daily habits (organization, scanning/entry discipline, discrepancy follow-up)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform periodic cycle counts and support inventory organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and restock shipping supplies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate professionally with customers, vendors, carriers, and internal teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow documented processes, and proactively suggest improvements when you see a better way&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Success in this role looks like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shipments go out on time, with correct parts and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inventory records match reality because discrepancies are caught early and resolved&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You take ownership of open items and close the loop without needing repeated follow-up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You learn quickly, ask good questions, and steadily improve how the operation runs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Required:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable using computers and Microsoft Office (especially Outlook and Excel)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail; you double-check your work and catch mistakes before they ship&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable, organized, and able to prioritize tasks in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear, professional communication and a team-first attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to learn new tools and follow process (we can train you on our systems)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Preferred:&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with shipping/receiving, fulfillment, or operations (small parts/electronics a plus)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with an ERP system (Microsoft Dynamics 365 is a plus)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with international shipping documentation is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job details&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Part-time, in person (Seattle)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schedule: weekday daytime hours (specifics can be discussed)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
