&lt;ul class=&quot;zqeyHd&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;LevrW&quot;&gt;Pay: $24.00 - $28.00 per hour&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;LevrW&quot;&gt;Expected hours: 20 per week&lt;/li&gt;
