&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated Supplier Quality Engineer to join our procurement team in a fast-paced and dynamic company. This position is based in &lt;strong data-start=&quot;228&quot; data-end=&quot;257&quot;&gt;Windhoek, Namibia&lt;/strong&gt;. You will monitor our suppliers and ensure they meet the required quality standards. With a pragmatic and entrepreneurial mindset, you will drive quality improvements and support our continued growth. If you have solid experience in quality assurance and quality control in electronics and PCBA manufacturing, a good understanding of ISO 9001:2015, and are eager to join an ambitious team, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Roles &amp;amp; Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
