&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;668&quot; data-local-id=&quot;18ddf933646e&quot;&gt;We are looking for a passionate and talented UI/UX Designer to help shape the future of our products and customer experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;796&quot; data-local-id=&quot;66d6f447ff8a&quot;&gt;This role is focused on understanding our users deeply and transforming those insights into intuitive, elegant, and impactful product experiences. The ideal candidate combines strong research skills, design thinking, visual design sensibilities, and a natural curiosity about how people interact with technology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1110&quot; data-local-id=&quot;6e1e89118673&quot;&gt;You will work closely with Product Management, Engineering, and R&amp;amp;D teams to design experiences that help customers succeed while driving product adoption and business outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1289&quot; data-local-id=&quot;9624ce41b574&quot;&gt;Our primary focus is on designing experiences for our SaaS &lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_kqswh2mm&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_5pioz8co _189e1dm9 _1il9buyh _19lc184f _d0altlke&quot; data-testid=&quot;definition-highlighter&quot;&gt;IoT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; platform, Torizon Cloud ecosystem and related products.&lt;/p&gt;
