&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1464&quot; data-local-id=&quot;0675c54424c9&quot;&gt;Develop a deep understanding of our target customers, their goals, workflows, motivations, and challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1464&quot; data-local-id=&quot;0675c54424c9&quot;&gt;Conduct user interviews, usability studies, surveys, and observational research.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1464&quot; data-local-id=&quot;0675c54424c9&quot;&gt;Identify customer pain points, unmet needs, and opportunities for innovation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1464&quot; data-local-id=&quot;0675c54424c9&quot;&gt;Build empathy for users and become an internal advocate for customer needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1464&quot; data-local-id=&quot;0675c54424c9&quot;&gt;Stay connected with customers throughout the product lifecycle to validate assumptions and gather feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;Product-Design&quot; data-local-id=&quot;5bf2c8568806&quot; data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1929&quot;&gt;Product Design&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1947&quot; data-local-id=&quot;a47f7c3babd5&quot;&gt;Transform complex technical workflows into intuitive and user-friendly experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1947&quot; data-local-id=&quot;a47f7c3babd5&quot;&gt;Create user journeys, workflows, wireframes, prototypes, and high-fidelity designs.&lt;
